                <h1>Essential Steps: Background Check Before Job Offer</h1>
                <p>Conducting a background check before extending a job offer is crucial for ensuring a safe and reliable hiring process. It helps employers verify the candidate's qualifications, work history, and criminal record, mitigating risks and fostering a trustworthy workplace. This step is essential for making informed hiring decisions.</p>
